{"tid":1629711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行既目的就係明知匪共會BLOCK尻你，你都要行完","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:08:15.000Z","uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45d1e64c51cacafb4880aea1cd8430e0d0528f2d","tid":1629711,"uid":277913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:16:40.000Z","msg":"日又叫人散水，夜又叫人散水，遊行行唔完又散水<br />\n你PLAN 好路線又唔諗著行完， 咁你PLAN 乜尻嘢遊行啫<br />\n你咪死返屋企瞓覺囉<br />\n和平遊行，和你老母咩<br />\n見到匪公安BLOCK你就鳥獸散，咁你行一千、一萬次都會係咁撚樣<br />\n你哋無決一戰既覺悟，又何來反抗啊<br />\n日日都抱住僥倖，日日都唔係END GAME<br />\n咁最後咪就係GAME OVER囉<br />\n今日港匪就係話你聽，以後都無和平遊行架喇<br />\n你一係就從此尻縮，一係就博命<br />\n無第二條路<br />\n如果我有講錯歡迎屌柒我，如果係勇敢抵抗過匪公安先撤退，我願意被人屌<br />\n證明香港仲有救"},{"pid":"4382b3dcf9b8cb528bb9b49efc9a3610a3ce0db7","tid":1629711,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:17:03.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lJMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=f7b929af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"7f48be8047043cf1a0fd0ee913445e0195086e2f","tid":1629711,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］全民起動 三罷民意調查<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們暫時收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=zkxump%2F